               <p>Westminster. On the night of the 16th of August I saw the prisoner take a dish of pork from my shop—I followed, and the policeman had him when I came up.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner. Q.</hi> Did you say anything to me? <hi rend="italic">A.</hi> I did not—I had left customers in my shop.</p>
